  <fr:p>We fix pairs <fr:tex>\mathopen {} \left ( a,b \right ) \mathclose {}</fr:tex> and <fr:tex>\mathopen {} \left ( a',b' \right ) \mathclose {}</fr:tex> in <fr:tex>\mathchoice { \textstyle \sum _{ \mathopen {} \left ( x:A \right ) \mathclose {} } }{ \textstyle \sum _{ \mathopen {} \left ( x:A \right ) \mathclose {} } }{ \scriptstyle \sum _{ \mathopen {} \left ( x:A \right ) \mathclose {} } }{ \scriptscriptstyle \sum _{ \mathopen {} \left ( x:A \right ) \mathclose {} } } {Bx}</fr:tex>. By <fr:ref
